  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play 7 kinds of games! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for bonus collectibles and extra hidden object challenges! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make matches, find details, memory, montage, and swap tiles, too! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through the game in any order you want! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 extra bonus levels! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wallpapers also included!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just Find It 4 has new, exciting puzzles! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through the exciting new levels, you can expect many new scenes and minigames. Spend hours exploring the game and solving its difficult puzzles.  As you make your way through each level, your abilities and attention to detail will be put to the test! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710070/extras/51460fc7454d3d875bb900c171a5dbd4.poster.avif?t=1739044878\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710070/extras/51460fc7454d3d875bb900c171a5dbd4.webm?t=1739044878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710070/extras/23e50a88d1d808eb2eab732e5f0405ac.poster.avif?t=1739044878\" width=620 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710070/extras/23e50a88d1d808eb2eab732e5f0405ac.webm?t=1739044878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710070/extras/23e50a88d1d808eb2eab732e5f0405ac.mp4?t=1739044878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710070/extras/c35b8267eabfddc203965fc899a4371e.poster.avif?t=1739044878\" width=620 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710070/extras/c35b8267eabfddc203965fc899a4371e.webm?t=1739044878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710070/extras/c35b8267eabfddc203965fc899a4371e.mp4?t=1739044878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just Find It 4 has something for everyone, regardless of experience. This is a must-play, so try it now!</p>",
